## 💳 Purchase & Activation

To purchase Fylrook and activate your license:

1. Send an email to our helpdesk at:  
   **[helpdesk.interpretationsoft@gmail.com](mailto:helpdesk.interpretationsoft@gmail.com)**

2. Include the following information in your email:
   - Your **full name**
   - Your **email address**
   - Any questions about Fylrook

3. You will receive instructions for payment and your **license key** to activate the software.

> After purchase, follow the included instructions to activate Fylrook and start organizing your files instantly.
